  "title": "supervisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Provide personalized skincare and beauty advice to customers</li>\n  <li>Demonstrate and promote products to achieve sales targets</li>\n  <li>Maintain high standards of customer service and product knowledge</li>\n  <li>Perform basic skin analysis to recommend suitable products</li>\n  <li>Assist in stock replenishment and visual merchandising</li>\n  <li>Ensure outlet cleanliness and proper product display</li>\n  <li>Handle cashiering duties and daily sales reporting</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Strong passion for the beauty industry</li>\n  <li>Retail or beauty experience is an advantage,</li>\n</ul>\n<p>need to work late in evening, weekends and public holidays; work according to company requirements</p>\n<p>If you have an interest in applying for this role, please WhatsApp me at 98198786 to apply. Only shortlisted candidates will be notified. Priority will be given to Singaporeans</p>\n<p>Young hon Lim/ manager</p>\n<p>Render private limited</p>\n<p>EA licence no 15c7827</p>\n<p>EA reg no R1550906</p>",
